    </div>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-6">As the table shows, FPA is highly seasonal. Households that consume heavily in winter (electric heaters, geysers) face FPA rates 5–10× higher than in summer — making winter the most expensive time to be an electricity consumer in Pakistan.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold mt-8 mb-4">How to Check FPA on Your Current Bill</h2>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Use our bill checker to pull your current month's bill — the FPA line is clearly labeled in the surcharges section, usually between "FC Surcharge" and "Electricity Duty". You can also check the exact NEPRA determination at <strong>nepra.org.pk → Decisions → Monthly FCA</strong> for the specific month.</p>

